(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 355.6 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 34f1c299-059f-5a0a-92ea-b6c24bc5d361))
(text "EC enumerates over Mu USB2_P3 only after the carrier-generated physical INTERNAL_USB_VBUS is above the supervisor threshold. U61 defaults disconnected so an always-powered EC cannot back-drive an off host PHY." (at 20.32 363.22 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid f4804344-4267-5095-bb44-ebf984d4d0d7))
(text "The verified B160QAN03.K panel is non-touch; USB2_P4 is paired with native USB-C port 2." (at 20.32 370.84 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 97253778-b565-5464-89f0-7dbc137e603d))
(text "Trackpad uses Mu USB2_P8 as a direct internal USB HID device. TRACKPAD_FAULT_N is pulled up to the EC; S3 removes trackpad VBUS, so wake-from-trackpad is not supported." (at 20.32 378.46 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid e682beb9-c095-50d5-bc43-f8f48095e6cb))
(text "The Intehill controller remains a bench fixture/fallback and is not populated on the motherboard." (at 20.32 386.08 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ba370de4-f346-5cd9-9561-ea361b0d27f9))
(text "J52 is released for Delta BFB04512HHA-CZ0T: fused MU_12V, 8.2k/3.9n FG interface, and 25kHz open-drain PWM. Floating PWM commands full speed; firmware never drives the fan PWM node high." (at 20.32 393.7 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 19a880ea-49cf-5ef9-960d-2c5971ae0bd2))
(text "Delta contract: 0.26A maximum, 35% minimum start duty, FG is open collector at 2 pulses/revolution, and 0% PWM stops the fan. Gate pull-down makes an unpowered/reset EC command full fan speed, not fan-off." (at 20.32 401.32 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ad7debc9-4795-59f3-82c7-051927676554))
(text "Thermal control has separate skin/hinge and Mu heatsink NTCs on ADC-capable EC pins." (at 20.32 408.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 73282620-21b8-51bf-bb3a-f7df4837b49f))
(text "The blower shares MU_12V: it is available whenever the Mu is powered. Thermal policy commands full fan and host throttle/shutdown before any final MU_12V cut; after a cut the passive coldplate/heatpipe/fin stack absorbs residual heat while heat generation is removed." (at 20.32 416.56 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 4c888a56-dbbc-59f8-81d0-2e6e8a2f6aab))
(text "Cooling default is copper spreader/heatpipe/vapor chamber plus the released Delta blower; no Peltier/TEC in the base design. Solid-state AirJet-style modules are a future mechanical option only." (at 20.32 424.18 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid cc0c0052-d84b-5911-b7bd-6294e4149f40))
